title: *PATREON PREVIEW* The Ballad of Horny Jimmy
description:
Thursday can only mean one thing: the running of the boys. The Core Four are back in the booth and things are getting real. After some tasty housekeeping and a patented peak behind the proverbial curtain for our best friends behind the paywall, we’re diving deep into matters of the heart, body and mind. The most transparent podcast in the universe has never been more clear on this Patreon-exclusive boyz only edition of The Only Podcast That Matters™.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
